author: cbs8
title: No top winners in Easy 5, Lotto or Powerball
text:
BATON ROUGE, La. (AP) - The Louisiana Lottery Corp. says nobody won three big weekend games in Louisiana. That means Wednesday's estimated jackpots rise to $70,000 for Easy 5, $300,000 for Lotto and $90 million for the Powerball.
The biggest prize won Saturday for any of those three games in Louisiana was $1,865. The lottery corporation says 13 Lotto tickets won that amount by matching five of six Lotto numbers.
Saturday night's winning numbers were:
Easy 5: 05-14-24-34-36
Lotto: 02-05-13-17-25-33
Powerball: 48-49-57-62-69, Powerball 19, Power Play 3
